FBIS3-38109 "drweu020_b_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 BENELUX Claes To Sue Newspaper Over Agusta Allegations LD3001140094 Brussels Radio Vlaanderen International in English 1330 GMT 30 Jan 94 LD3001140094 Brussels Radio Vlaanderen International Language: English Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] Foreign Minister Willy Claes intends to sue the newspaper HET LAATSTE NIEUWS for libel. The minister announced this in BRTN's Sunday morning [30 January] television program The Seventh Day. HET LAATSTE NIEUWS yesterday wrote that Claes had been in favor of accepting a 15 million franc bribe from the Italian helicopter company Agusta. [passage omitted] Minister Claes has fervently denied his involvement and says he never even discussed bribes with the Agusta company.
